Key Match Events: Denver Nuggets held San Antonio Spurs scoreless until 2:11 left in overtime with a 7-0 run.
Nikola Jokic's successful free throw extended the Nuggets' lead to 108-106 with less than a minute to play.
Devin Vassell missed a two-pointer but recovered his own rebound and put-back to send the game into overtime tied 108-108.
Victor Wembanyama recorded his first 20-20 game of the season with 20 points and 23 rebounds, along with three assists and four blocks.
